{"tid":1395962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"物資同我入黎！！","createTime":"2019-08-02T02:30:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T03:05:25.000Z","uid":226103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fe2bb55e99f4d8b4827dba025c8edb7faddf0d31","tid":1395962,"uid":226103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:30:33.000Z","msg":"聽日就係旺角再遊行啦！！！<br />\n雖然班狗唔肯批不反對通知書<br />\n只係批晏架街足球場嘅集會<br />\n但我地都要做好準備，睇返上幾次場war game <br />\n有唔少喺前線嘅手足唔夠裝備<br />\n相反喺物資鏈同中間嘅手足有豬咀、頭盔同眼罩<br />\n所以我喺度求大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定一定要將有用嘅物資留比前線呀</span></span><br />\n記得唔上前線嘅話 普通口罩都頂得住 當然重要加返頂帽啦！！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bkcFfZM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbkcFfZM.png&h=44869708&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AvPHujN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAvPHujN.png&h=5b4e3e87&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5a4142d7dcd3a30c3d9fcbb9ff5c92de02074a3","tid":1395962,"uid":226103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:31:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62a4b9971c6cb046131a50b53188cf72adba4d21","tid":1395962,"uid":226103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:31:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"94de25d1b0e8e9a538992af90388de0cbd4f15b7","tid":1395962,"uid":226103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:31:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f80fc9a0ec